item.description:
Gone are the days when a comedienne's material was limited to PMS, menopause and the shortcomings of the men in their lives. The 5 Funny Females Comedy Tour is hosted by Susan Alexander, and brings a lineup of five women having varied ethnic backgrounds and comedic types. The tour is refined yet quirky. These laugh inducing women show off their unique points of view as they engage the audience with their offbeat life stories and opinions. The comics will take the stage at 8:30 pm at Atkinson Resort and Country Club on Saturday October 22nd.

The line up on October 22nd at The Atkinson Resort will include:

Susan Alexander - The Denial Show, Comedy Time

Andrea Henry - Nick at Nite

Naomi Ekperigin - VH1

Kendra Cunningham - Late Night with Jimmy Fallon, SNL

Chantal Carrere - ABC, truTV


5. Doors will open at 7 PM with a three course Chef prepared buffet dinner show. Tickets are general admission and cost $55 for the dinner show. For show only, tickets are $25 and doors open at 8:15 pm.. A cash bar is available. They can be purchased at via Guest Services at 603-362-8700.
